- Contract driven 
- HTTP methods / verbs - POST, PUT, PATCH, GET, DELETE, HEAD, OPTIONS, TRACE, TRACK
- Status codes-
	- 1xx
	- 2xx--> 200-OK, 201-created, 204- no content
	- 3xx--> redirectional 
	- 4xx --> 400, 401, 402,403,404,409,415
	- 5xx--> 500,501,502,503,504

- auth types
	- basic auth - base 64 encoding
	- API keys - 
	- Token -
	- Oauth - JWT-json web token, bearer



